General.Name: Spectur Ltd
General.Description: Spectur Limited designs, develops, manufactures, and sells solar remote sensing, thinking, and acting solutions in Australia. The company offers wireless camera systems, including STA6, a solar camera system for monitoring critical sites, deterring and warning danger, and building custom sensing solutions; HD5, a camera system for security, surveillance, time-lapse capture, and safety and warning; SWC5, a camera system for beach management, shark warnings, and smart city applications; and mobile surveillance accessories, including trailers and bases, solar-powered lighting, sensors, and smart devices. The company's products are used in Engineering, construction and building, government, and utility sectors. Spectur Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Welshpool, Australia.
